idiot is a 1992 hindi film based on fyodor dostoevsky 's novel , the idiot . it was directed by mani kaul and starred shah rukh khan and ayub khan-din . the film debuted at the new york film festival in october 1992 . in this version of the tale , placed in contemporary mumbai , prince &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( khan-din ) is a man whose epilepsy is mistaken for &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; .